org.anchoranalysis.spatial.box

Class BoundingBoxContains

  • Object
    • BoundingBoxContains

  • public final class BoundingBoxContains
extends Object
    Does a bounding box contain other objects?

    The other objects can be points, other bounding boxes etc.

    Author:
    Owen Feehan
